# Copy to .env.local and uncomment to override defaults.
# Bun loads .env.local automatically before every command — no extra config needed.

# Renderer selection (Electrobun)
# Default: CEF (Chromium) — consistent cross-platform rendering, avoids WebKitGTK bugs.
# Set to "webkit" to use WebKitGTK on Linux / WKWebView on macOS for debugging renderer-specific issues.
# ROADRAVEN_RENDERER=webkit
